data.description: 4.25% ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE!!! Introducing a charming 3-bedroom gem in the active adult Sun City! Perfectly positioned on a generous corner lot, this home offers both spacious and low-maintenance outdoor spaces. Discover a welcoming living & dining room combo and a formal family room w/a vaulted ceiling! Tile flooring in common areas, neutral paint t/out, and soft carpet in bedrooms are some features worth mentioning. The kitchen has a travertine backsplash and ample wood cabinetry. Have a good night's sleep in the bright bedrooms, with one boasting a walk-in closet! Out the back, you have a covered patio to relax and room for enjoying BBQ. Located close to Fairway and Mountain View Recreation Centers, you'll have easy access to amenities like tennis, indoor walking paths, pool, spa, & more!
